long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Fiverr sellers data from the search page to a XLS/CSV file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open an Fiverr search page.
2️⃣ Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2️⃣ Export on multiple search pages simultaneous.
3️⃣ Export listing data for current item to a xls/csv file, data include:  Gig Id, Gig Url, Buying Review Rating, Buying Review Rating Count, Is Featured, Is Fiverr Choice, Is Pro, Price, Seller Id, Seller Country, Seller Display Name, Seller Img, Seller Languages, Seller Level, Seller Name, Seller Rating Count, Seller Rating Score, Seller Url, Status, Title, Type, Origin Search Url.

🎯 Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your business data management and make informed decisions with Fiverr  Seller Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Fiverr ❗️🔒
